These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, cooking, drawing, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, adventure, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, parkour, rugby, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, scooter, ship
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
 2. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##8
 5. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 8. the person watching action movies is between the person driving the roller and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 9. the person driving the ship is the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
13. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
14. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person driving the scooter##1
15. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person who's sport is parkour##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games     | cooking   | board-games | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action   | spy   | adventure  |
| Sport         | parkour  | rugby  | surfing  | soccer |
| Transport     | subway    | scooter | roller     | ship    |

