.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: onion, cherry, pineapple, artichoke
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, funk, ambient, soul
4 different pets are kept: cat, bird, horse, pony
 1. the fan of ambient is between the owner of the cat and the fan of funk##2
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
 5. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the fan of funk##8
 6. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 8. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of punk is the owner of the bird##1
10. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
11. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
14. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating onion##1
17. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan of funk##8
18. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
19. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | tea | mirinda  | soy-milk  |
| Food          | artichoke     | cherry | onion | pineapple  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | ambient  | soul | punk |
| Pet           | horse | pony | cat    | bird  |

