 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
 7. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
