.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, artichoke, nectarine, blueberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, hiking, traveling, dancing
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, police-officer, lawyer, photographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, cricket, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the accountant##6
 2. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 3. the person eating blueberry is the lawyer##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is between the accountant and the police-officer##2
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person eating artichoke##8
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the photographer##1
10. the police-officer is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the right of the person eating pineapple##8
12. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
