10. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
11. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching musical movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
13. the chinese is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
