The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, helicopter, taxi
 1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the mechanic##8
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 5. the person driving the helicopter is the egyptian##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the german##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda is not the indian##6
 8. the bartender is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking mirinda##7
 9. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
10. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the bartender##3
11. the scientist is on the right of the police-officer##1
12. the bartender is not the indonesian##6
13. the german is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the bartender##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
