 7. the egyptian is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 8. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 9. the fan of country is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of punk##7
10. the fan of country is not to the left of the american##8
11. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
