The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bike, tram, snowmobile
 1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 2. the person driving the ship is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 4. the police-officer is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking fanta##7
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 8. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
 9. the journalist is on the far left or far right##3
10. the security-guard is not to the left of the security-guard##8
11. the journalist is on the far left##1
12. the mechanic is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
15. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
16. the security-guard is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
