The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, airplane, jet-ski
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
10. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
11. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice   | fanta     | hot-chocolate    | milk |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | country      | house     | dubstep     |
| Sport         | rugby | water-polo  | ice-hockey     | volleyball  |
| Transport     | taxi     | airplane | jet-ski | subway     |

