 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
 3. the person drinking milk is the fan of soul##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 8. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 9. the egyptian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
10. the fan of punk is not the pakistani##6
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
12. the turkish is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
14. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of punk##1

