 2. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the fisherman##8
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
 6. the person driving the train is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the engineer is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
 8. the accountant is on the far right##1
 9. the fisherman is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
12. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
13. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the engineer##8

.:: Answer ::.
