.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, writing, gardening
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, accountant, entrepreneur, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, satire, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, blues, techno, dubstep
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the pilot##8
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
 4. the manager is the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is not the entrepreneur##6
 6. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
 7. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8
 8. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 9. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is writing is between the entrepreneur and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening    | writing   | woodworking   | chess |
| Job           | pilot | accountant    | entrepreneur | manager    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | thriller | musical     | zombie    |
| Music-Genre   | country   | techno      | blues         | dubstep     |

 